  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/8002538e049411f2f492f2ce7e855b8d.poster.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/8002538e049411f2f492f2ce7e855b8d.webm?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/8002538e049411f2f492f2ce7e855b8d.mp4?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Chloé’s Requiem</i> is a Japanese 2D adventure game, filled with mysteries and surprises. The young creator, in her teens, created the original game, inspired by free game titles such as <i>The Witch’s House</i> and <i>Ao Oni</i>. <br><br>From the original release in 2013, the graphics and sounds have all been completely revamped, allowing all players, new and returning, to have a fresh experience with the game. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/5a651f6072d19ab00cae866b1b1193d0.poster.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/5a651f6072d19ab00cae866b1b1193d0.webm?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/5a651f6072d19ab00cae866b1b1193d0.mp4?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/80af8218073ac5e3405bfcea0f25446a.poster.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/80af8218073ac5e3405bfcea0f25446a.webm?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/80af8218073ac5e3405bfcea0f25446a.mp4?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Interactions between Michél the violinist and Chloé the pianist can be enjoyed with beautiful character illustrations.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/6b90ad79cf2ab84899ce5e2a76f2cf4c.poster.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/6b90ad79cf2ab84899ce5e2a76f2cf4c.webm?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>To break the multiple \"curses\" in the mansion, the player may need to hold items in both hands. There may be \"curses\" that require musical knowledge, making music one of the central themes of the game. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/baf81d124e44e2777e10cdc216628142.poster.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/baf81d124e44e2777e10cdc216628142.webm?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The world is set in 19th century Europe, with aesthetics and interiors reflecting the era.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/fe9e97a36b6515c32c15d32ec6cbd553.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=156 /></span><br>We are all looking forward to your arrival.",
